               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; members of the Trinity (fols. 44va, 49vb, 50va, 52ra); names of the donor and his family members; groups of lines on the incipit page; incipit of all (sub)sections; elements of the punctuation signs and of text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>For each month, the miracles include the following ʾarke-hymns:</note>
                     <note>I-1) እንበለ፡ ሕማም፡ አምላክ፡ አመ፡ ከመ፡ ዮም። ... (fol. 15va-16ra)</note>
                     <note>I-2) ኦዘሐወጽኮሙ፡ ለደቂቀ፡ ሥርዓት፡ ሠለስቱ። ... (fol. 24ra-va)</note>
                     <note>I-3) ኦዘረዳእኮ፡ ለቴዎድሮስ፡ መዋዒ። ... (fol. 34va-vb)</note>
                     <note>I-4) ኦዘወሀብኮ፡ እምአፈ፡ በላዒ፡ መብልዓ። ... (fols. 39vb-40rb)</note>
                     <note>I-5) ኦዘተዘለፍኮ፡ ለበለዓም፡ ውስተ፡ ፍኖቱ። ... (fol. 56rb-va)</note>
                     <note>I-6) ኦዘባላሕኮሙ፡ በወርኃ፡ ሚያዝያ፡ ባልሆ። ... (fol. 64ra)</note>
                     <note>I-7) ኦእንተ፡ ፆርከ፡ በክሳድ፡ አኃዜ። ... (fol. 68vb)</note>
                     <note>I-8) ኦዘአጽናእከ፡ እም፡ ኃጕለ፡ ድቀት፡ ወትንታኔ። ... (fol. 86vb)</note>
                     <note>I-9) ኦዘቀተልኮ፡ ለሰናክሬም፡ ጸአሌ። ፈጣሬ።... (fols. 94vb-95ra)</note>
                     <note>I-10) ኦዘአጽናእኮ፡ ለቍስጣንጢኖስ፡ ኃሣሤ። ... (fol. 104ra)</note>
                     <note>I-11) ኦዘፈወስኮ፡ ለሕዝቅያስ፡ እምደዊሁ። ... (fols. 11<ref type="mss" corresp="ES0vb111">0vb-111</ref>ra)</note>
                     <note>I-12) ኦዘኃደጎ፡ ለዘኃደጎ፡ መንፈሱ። ወዳዊትሃ፡ ዓቀብከ። ... (fol. 118rb).</note>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="coloph1">
