                        <locus/> 
                        <foreign xml:lang="en">Fol. 119va: This book was written in the time of Säbʾa Gadǝs and qes gäbäz Kidanä Dǝngǝl. The one who purchased it is ʿabeto Wäldä Gärima with 12 ʾAläba.The one who stole this book or erased it...
 </foreign>
                        <note/>
                     </colophon>
