                           <locus target="#119va">Fol. 119va</locus>: Donation note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 119va-vb: ወለዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘተጽሕፈት፡ በዘመነ፡ ሰብአ፡ ጋድስ፡ ወቂስ፡ ገበዝ፡ ኪዳነ፡ ድንግል፡ ዘተሣየጣ፡ ዓቤቶ፡ ወልደ፡ ገሪማ፡ በ፲ወ፪አለባ፡ ለዛ[fol. 119vb]ቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘሠረቃ፡ ወዘፈሐቃ፡...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note, written in the main hand, states that the Ms. was purchased by ʾabeto Wäldä Gärima for the price of 12 ʾalaba (?) and donated to the church of Our Lady Mary of Saʾet. The note mentiones also the names of his wife and children.
                        </item>
